<center><h2><a name="contests">Contests</a></h2></center>
<ul>
<Li><A HREF = "limerick/limerick.html"><b><i>The Toast Point
Limerick
Contest!</A></i></b><br>

<i>...well, if that's poetry, I don't like poetry...</i><br>

Separated into <I>naughty</I> and <I>squeaky-clean</I> categories.
<p>

<li>
<b><i><a href="haiku/haiku.html">The Toast Point Haiku
Contest!</a></i></b><br>

<i>...and surmounted with something Japanese - it matters not
what...</I><br>

Enjoy the nuggets of wisdom of other contestants!  Enter your
own!<p>



<li><a href="fiction/fiction.html"><b><i>The Toast Point Bad
Fiction Contest!</a></i></b><br>

You, too, can write juicy stories opening with <i>"Snarling,
Delilah slammed 

the receiver down and ripped the phone out of the wall.  Sulking,
she lit a cigarette 

and gazed at the stained ceiling"</i>.  See the results of other
twisted efforts!
</ul>
